{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_04_01",
  "title": "神崎莉央 1話 宣戦布告",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "living-01-000-night",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "すずが歌った麻奈のカバー曲、評判がいいみたいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looks like Suzu's cover of Mana's song is getting quite the buzz.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "うまく歌えなくて悩んでいたすずの背中を\n莉央さんが押してくれたおかげです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu was all knotted up about not being able to sing it right‚\nbut it was Rio-san’s encouragement that gave her a boost.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "私は軽くアドバイスしただけよ。それに\nどちらかというと、もう一方の話題の方が面白かったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All I did was give her a few pointers. Plus‚\nthe other topic we talked about was a lot more fascinatin'‚ to tell the truth.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "すずがあんなことを考えていたなんて……\n凄く微笑ましかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Never thought Suzu would come up with something like that…\nIt was downright delightful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "微笑ましいって、一体なんの話ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Delightful? What exactly are y'all referring to?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "それは……\n貴方には教えられないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That is…\nSomething I can't spill to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、ポテンシャルはあると思ってたけど\nちょっと助言しただけであそこまで歌えるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I believed in her potential‚ sure‚ but\nto think she'd nail it just with a smidge of advice…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "私達も負けていられないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Guess we can't be resting on our laurels either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "同じ事務所の仲間とも張り合うなんて\n相変わらず負けず嫌いですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Competing with folks from the same agency‚ huh?\nYou sure are as fiercely competitive as ever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、私達は負けない。星見プロは居心地がいいけど\nだからといって仲良しこよしをするつもりはないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Absolutely‚ we ain't in this to lose. Hoshimi Pro's comfy and all‚\nbut that don't mean we're gonna settle for just getting along.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "サニピや月スト、トリエルに勝って頂点に立つのは\n私達LizNoirよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's gonna be us‚ LizNoir‚ who beats Sunny Peace‚ Moon Tempest‚\nand TRINITYAiLE to the top.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "身近に競い合える相手がいるのはいいことです\nこれからもお互いに切磋琢磨していきましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Having rivals close by to challenge you is a blessin'.\nLet's both keep on improving and pushing each other.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.5000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "……私は宣戦布告のつもりだったんだけど\n貴方と話してると毒気を抜かれるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I meant to be making a declaration of war‚ but\ntalking to you always takes the edge off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく、私達がさらに飛躍するために\nこれからはいろんな仕事を取って来てちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ for us to leap even higher‚\nbring us all sorts of jobs‚ will ya?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いろんな仕事、ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All sorts of jobs?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirが進化するためには\n様々なことにもっと挑戦するべきだと思うの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For LizNoir to evolve‚\nI think we need to take on even more challenges.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "だからどんな仕事でも遠慮なく入れなさい\n貴方が取ってきた仕事なら文句は言わないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So don't hold back on any job‚\nI won't complain about anything you bring to us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.1086517334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "そのくらいには貴方のことを信用してるんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's how much I trust you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そこまで言われたら\n信頼に応えない訳にはいきませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you put it that way‚\nI have to live up to that trust‚ don't I?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ちょうど仕事の依頼がきたんです。莉央さんに\nオーディション番組の審査員をしてほしいそうです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ we just got a job offer for you‚ Rio-san.\nThey want you to be a judge on an audition show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　審査員じゃ歌えないじゃない\n私はパフォーマーなのよ。歌える仕事がいいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? If I'm judgin'‚ I can't sing‚ can I?\nI'm a performer. I want jobs where I can sing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ダメですか……それじゃあ\nテレビの生放送特番で歌番組をやるんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's no good‚ huh… Then how about\na TV live broadcast special music program…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "生放送……一発勝負の緊張感の中で歌うのね\n面白そうじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Live broadcast… Singing in the thrill of a one-shot deal.\nSounds intriguing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、そうじゃなくて\n歌番組の司会をしてほしいというオファーです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ not quite.\nThey want you to host the music program.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "歌わせなさいよ！　却下よ！\n全部素敵な仕事だけど、今はそうじゃないのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let me sing! Declined!\nAll wonderful jobs‚ but that's not what I'm looking for now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.1333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 147.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、少しいいですか？\n今までとは毛色の違う仕事のオファーがきてるんですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ can I have a moment?\nWe’ve got an offer for a job that’s a bit different from what we’re used to.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "毛色の違う仕事？\n今度はちゃんとした内容でしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A different kind of job?\nThis time it better be something proper.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "仕事の内容は、新作映画のプロモーションです\n舞台挨拶やイベントに出演して映画のPRをするんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The job is to promote a new movie.\nYou’d be appearing at stage greetings and events to do PR for the movie.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "宣伝するのはケイト・ローレンスが出演する\nアクション映画『トレジャー・ライダー』の続編で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s the sequel to the action movie\n\"Treasure Rider\" starring Kate Lawrence…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
