    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "歌えない仕事ですけど、いいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a job that doesn’t involve singing‚ is that okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio021.m4a",
      "text": "それとこれとは話が別よ！\nケイティの映画の宣伝なら喜んでやらせてもらうわ！",
      "translations": {
