      "text": "『トレジャー・ライダー』は演技派女優だった彼女が\n過酷な肉体改造を行ってアクションに挑んだ快作よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Treasure Rider\" is a brilliant piece where she‚ known for her acting chops‚\nunderwent a tough physical transformation to take on action roles.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
