      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_04_01-rio024.m4a",
      "text": "なんてこと……。ケイティをろくに知らないなんて\nそれでよく芸能関係者を名乗れたわね！",
